-846360136.text: "The most important gene changes with gain of function belonging to PanIN : RAS, EGFR, COX-2, HGF, FADK, Notch, Wnt, Myb, CCKRB, BCL-6, CXCR4, AKT-2, and the genes with loss of function promote pre-cancerous lesions : BRCA2, PTEN, SMAD4, p16, p53, p21 and WAF, p27 and CIP1."
